{"tid":1551315,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"楊凡動畫《繼園臺七號》奪威尼斯影展最佳劇片 楊凡：奇怪的力量以人權之名 讓我們甚至無法自由搭乘大眾交通工具","createTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:21:48.000Z","uid":276779,"like":4,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"35e230f6fb419da598f1fc9e2137fdbdf343048f","tid":1551315,"uid":276779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"又一廢老<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1rPDOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1rPDOM.png&h=14011fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有依個大陸訪問：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mtime.com/2019/09/05/1596833-3.html?fbclid=IwAR0dNjyzEmdsRvBu0lWkelWG87hk1ZcajCvg14JIBQXNqr7XLhNul_H0FQs#content\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mtime.com%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F1596833-3.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0dNjyzEmdsRvBu0lWkelWG87hk1ZcajCvg14JIBQXNqr7XLhNul_H0FQs%23content&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprt7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=6c55c6dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mtime.com/2019/09/05/1596833-3.html?fbclid=IwAR0dNjyzEmdsRvBu0lWkelWG87hk1ZcajCvg14JIBQXNqr7XLhNul_H0FQs#content</a><br />\n<br />\n「1967年这里发生了抗议活动，在6个月的时间里香港发生了翻天覆地的变化，警察和英国军队试图镇压。而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大约两个月前，整个事件又在重演。这些抗议活动以&ldquo;自由&rdquo;、&ldquo;人权&rdquo;和&ldquo;民主&rdquo;的名义出现，所有这些美妙的字眼都把香港搞得天翻地覆。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我那时候20岁在香港学习，那时香港还是英国的殖民地，我从来不知道什么是人权，我也不知道民主会是什么样子。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但是现在，在这些日子里，你拥有了一切，用那些美丽的名字再次把香港搞得天翻地覆。而且我认为媒体&mdash;&mdash;不仅是西方媒体还有香港媒体&mdash;&mdash;他们的报道有很大的偏见，</strong></span>因为每个故事都有两面，你不应该只报道故事的一面，这让我很难过。」<br />\n<br />\n套戲9月26號上映，罷睇就基本，唔知有冇宣傳活動，大家諗下方法招待下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdd272030478ada16bad9bbcad7f2228447abec","tid":1551315,"uid":276779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"44a726cb246d8e03e07d43771637b5ee5b43710a","tid":1551315,"uid":276779,"like":0,"di